FROM (
    SELECT prescriptions.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC) AS C1 
    FROM prescriptions 
    WHERE prescriptions.subject_id IN (
        SELECT DISTINCT subject_id 
        FROM prescriptions 
        WHERE drug = 'pseudoephedrine' 
        AND strftime('%Y', starttime) = '2100'
    ) 
    AND strftime('%Y', starttime) = '2100' 
    GROUP BY prescriptions.drug
) AS T1 
WHERE T1.C1 <= 3
